{"type": "article", "id": 49730, "title": "施华洛世奇考虑 IPO，以及，Dior 开设首家眼镜专卖店 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-30T04:05:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 15714, "name": "龙珠"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 46422, "name": "diesel"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 4872, "name": "施华洛世奇"}, {"id": 45429, "name": "topshop"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180130104514qka8wOdX2KnmgUiR.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Topshop-and-Topman-manager-job-cuts-expected-soon,941496.html#.Wm_d9ZP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>实体店人流量减少，Topshop 和 Topman 或将大裁员</b></a> | 有消息称，由于实体店人流量减少，销售逐渐向电子端转移，Topshop 和 Topman 正在寻求更合理的店面战略，数百家门店或将进行裁员。目前，每家 Topshop 和 Topman 门店都有独立的经理，未来可能会变为一个总店经理负责两个品牌，以削减人力成本。 </p><p></p><p><a href=\"https://www.thestar.com/business/2018/01/29/swarovski-says-an-ipo-could-propel-jewellers-digital-growth.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>施华洛世奇称，会考虑 IPO</b></a> | Nadja Swarovski，施华洛世奇的第五代接班人、公司执行董事会成员日前在达沃斯经济论坛期间接受采访时表示，首次公开募股将有助于该品牌在北美地区提升其数字化形象和规模，但目前这一举措还未出台。去年，施华洛世奇的年销售额约为 34 亿欧元，全球门店约 2800 多家，中国是最大的市场。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/547154\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior 在巴黎蒙田大街开设了首家眼镜专卖店</a>。这家店临近 Dior 旗舰店，售卖 Dior 和 Dior Homme 系列和店铺限量版眼镜，另外还配有专业的验光师团队，可以为顾客进行一对一的视力检查。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105011GSUk5DYfNx04pEjB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105013CGEDsYpHgdkfPiNS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105011O3FxrlPjsfy9JRG6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105010RXZnvLDFcIKwS7QT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105011itvGPClOne4DxN3W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.672500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105011ckqCZz4Ww5GDgdTY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105009VCHzuYBA4ObJfw59.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105010KJUApYyqCfT8V5aj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-01-30/diesel-acmilan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DIESEL 发布了 AC 米兰最新的场下服装</a>，这系列采用了全新的黑红配色设计，包括夹克、T 恤、牛仔裤、包等多款单品。作为特别的联名系列，从现在开始它会在一部分的 DIESEL 门店发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018013010511195GDehrjUQq8nFby.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105114l1CgAEMYBonHiyXZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.198485\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105114s37ufcyIJtM59aLO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105114MRAg5iclzodm0awx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.469697\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105115YnSPq1e0oUDLZVM8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>我们之前报道过 adidas originals 可能会在今年秋天发布与《龙珠》联名款球鞋的消息，不过，直到现在都还没有透露官方的具体信息。 </p><p>有个名叫 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/dragonball-z-nike-collab-concept/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Walsh Design</a> 的插画师等不住了，他自己绘制了一系列《龙珠》和 Nike 联名款的球鞋，以 Nike 的热门鞋款 Air Max 97, Air Max 1, Air Max 90, Air VaporMax 为原型，根据 12 个动漫人物进行了不同的配色和主题创作，来看看： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105426w8LnYMA7eW4qduPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105434NPOjelnIGMZwvy4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801301054370aA2uMpk1exzX8KN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018013010543725aHoplGRIhvzCgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105438uRzXioeK18pgsEPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105438JLzCkRZaxhp3uVM5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105439qO0azFwbufNyLgYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105439DMF08tGZuzgSUeO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105440rKOxGCvPVnhfyQAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105440wm0OoScRQKnN5MBP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801301054429sNpiUAJtDHP35gO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>最近，诚品书店改造了台湾云林县斗六市的一间 80 多岁的老宅，开设了一间快闪书店，取名<a href=\"https://popbee.com/lifestyle/travel/eslite-old-book-store-pop-up/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“云梦制造所”</a>。书店内的书籍以讲述上世纪的台湾为主，如果你恰好在附近的话不妨去看看，这间快闪书店将持续至 2 月 25 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105522HBf6hFR0yKLwzVes.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105523dEMvjKtHP1gyAnDi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105526z6qDSKLM2cQXEoev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105527DHWF1sP7foYqpb0C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>还记得上周 Chanel 在巴黎浪漫花园里发布的 2018 春夏系列吗？ </p><p>事实上，除了缀满蕾丝和花朵的小裙子外，这一季的<a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/1/chanel-bags-spring-summer-2018-pre-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Chanel 的包包</a>也因为加入了冰淇淋色而变得清新了。比如你可以看到 Boy Chanel，Gabrielle 和经典的 Flap Bag，有了薄荷绿、淡蓝色、珊瑚色、渐变色... </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105647iD3dwBPYMkyb1hec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105647zuYdTB4ntISZRr1v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105659NKuRAE78nrjXiLlO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105746aXjswQbgvm21TGuN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105659EDKM9iNwTfVCkuah.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105659X6K2IlnuqF4Lhrme.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105659GFop92HSqvM03BUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105659jFlOW9yEkBpaDL4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105700Sz3usIZaTdCHFqvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105700QPjTJnBgchGkFUsY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105700z81xUJtS6rkMYpnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105700y28nDP5s3JmcLEtI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105700Dntz5YkVSyuIsHWA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105700AoH7VBPuOTNmIvX9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105701tGz4edLTWOwiVMyb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105701OYi8LTHAFl6kGKz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180130105701rLbDXyNks1zPa7d8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>